file.title: AMM PART II-1285 - CHAPTER 12-21-14-03 - AILERON&ELEVATOR DISCONNECT SYSTEM - SERVICING

page.data: AIRCRAFT MAINTENANCE MANUAL AILERON&ELEVATOR DISCONNECT SYSTEM - SERVICING EFFECTIVITY: ALL 1. General A. The procedures for the lubrication on the aileron disconnect system is given in AMM TASK 27-15-02-600-801-A/300 and on the elevator disconnect system is given in AMM TASK 27-35-00-600-801-A/300.
